name: The Giving Tree (Tewbi)
description:
Another game created for an APCS course, this time for the spring semester final project. As such, you will need Java to run it. Controls and instructions should be in the included guide.

OST can be found here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGGn61R7pz7ws-QZdK7ABimmISuHamNHj

Hope you enjoy!

Note: I have provided two different versions of the same game. One was compiled in Java 8 and the other was compiled in Java 16. If the Java 16 version does not work on your device because of compatibility issues, try the version compiled in Java 8.
